parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electric power steering assist can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn, leading to loss of control of the vehicle, which can result in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The power steering warning light illuminates
the steering wheel becomes difficult to turn
the vehicle loses power steering assist
the steering wheel seizes
the vehicle stalls
the speedometer gauges fluctuate
and the vehicle accelerates independently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The ignition key problems can cause the key to become stuck in the ignition, making it difficult or impossible to start or turn off the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The key gets stuck in the ignition
the key will not come out
the passlock light comes on
the car stalls while in motion
and the key has to be wiggled to get it back into the turn-off position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or shut off while driving, leading to a loss of power and increasing the risk of accidents. Additionally, the key may become stuck in the ignition, making it difficult or impossible to remove.
symptoms: The key becomes stuck in the ignition
the vehicle stalls or shuts off while driving
the ignition switch seizes
the vehicle will not start
and the key will not release from the ignition without force.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag light illuminates
the airbag fails to deploy in an accident
and the passenger airbag light flashes on and off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel system can cause the vehicle to stall or shut off while driving, leading to a loss of power and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts off while driving
the fuel cap needs to be opened and closed to restart the vehicle
and the fuel line leaks gasoline.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel system can cause fuel leaks, which can lead to fires, and potentially result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: Strong fuel odor inside and outside the vehicle
fuel leaks
difficulty starting the vehicle
and the check engine light and check gas cap light may illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump can cause fuel leaks, which can lead to fires, and potentially result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: Strong fuel odor inside and outside the vehicle
fuel leaks
difficulty starting the vehicle
and the check engine light and check gas cap light may illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel lines can cause fuel leaks, which can lead to fires, and potentially result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: Strong fuel odor inside and outside the vehicle
fuel leaks
difficulty starting the vehicle
and the check engine light and check gas cap light may illuminate.
